QuestData.Title: Revenge: Served Hot
QuestData.Description: Look, the boss might be keeping a level head here, but we should show these naga what happens when you mess with the Gob Squad. Don't you agree?$b$bThe naga are sending their behemoths to destroy what's left of our ship. Why don't you take my rocket launcher and make an example out of them. That'll send the message loud and clear!
QuestData.LogDescription: Use Ticker's Rocket Launcher to slay $1oa Vilescale Behemoths.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet with Ticker at the Forlorn Ruins.
